  cardName: "L\u1EA1c B\u1EA5t T\u01B0 Th\u1EE5c"
  cardImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ef7a8eb5b9336e54eb7044b8b558cad5, type: 3}
  cardDescription: "Giai \u0111o\u1EA1n h\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED9ng, b\u1EA1n s\u1EED
    d\u1EE5ng l\xE1 b\xE0i n\xE0y l\xEAn 1 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u01A1i kh\xE1c kh\xF4ng
    c\xF3 [L\u1EA1c B\u1EA5t T\u01B0 Th\u1EE5c] trong khu v\u1EF1c ph\xE1n x\xE9t
    c\u1EE7a h\u1ECD.\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1EA1n ph\xE1n x\xE9t c\u1EE7a m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
    ch\u01A1i, n\u1EBFu h\u1ECD c\xF3 [L\u1EA1c B\u1EA5t T\u01B0 Th\u1EE5c] trong
    khu v\u1EF1c ph\xE1n x\xE9t, h\u1ECD ti\u1EBFn h\xE0nh 1 l\u1EA7n ph\xE1n x\xE9t,
    n\u1EBFu k\u1EBFt qu\u1EA3 ph\xE1n x\xE9t tr\xEAn l\xE0:\r\nCh\u1EA5t \u2665:
    h\u1ECD b\u1ECF \u0111i l\xE1 b\xE0i n\xE0y.\r\nKh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i ch\u1EA5t
    \u2665: h\u1ECD b\u1ECF qua giai \u0111o\u1EA1n h\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED9ng trong
    l\u01B0\u1EE3t n\xE0y v\xE0 b\u1ECF \u0111i l\xE1 b\xE0i n\xE0y."
